Header.title: Seize the Means of Education
Header.paragraph: Promoting health literacy, providing mentoring, and fostering educational development in regional and remote areas.

About.paragraph: Serag and Soloman Saleh are junior doctors from Sydney who do stuff. Wellness ED is the result of their love for teaching alongside a passion for global and regional health.
